      <title>利比亚权力斗争加剧，央行陷入争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/libya-power-struggle-builds-as-central-bank-pulled-into-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚央行周一表示，将恢复运营，无视更换行长和董事会的决定，此举可能进一步危及该欧佩克国家敌对政府之间本已脆弱的停火协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/libya-power-struggle-builds-as-central-bank-pulled-into-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 12:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪将在俄罗斯入侵后首次访问乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/modi-will-visit-ukraine-for-first-time-since-russia-s-invasion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪定于周五访问基辅，试图平衡与华盛顿和莫斯科的关系，但已排除在调解俄罗斯结束乌克兰战争的角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/modi-will-visit-ukraine-for-first-time-since-russia-s-invasion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国反对终止对乌克兰援助的报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/germany-pushes-back-against-report-on-ending-ukraine-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[柏林财政部发言人表示，只要有必要，德国将继续支持乌克兰抵御俄罗斯的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/germany-pushes-back-against-report-on-ending-ukraine-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 10:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉面临巨额预算赤字并吓跑投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/lula-is-running-huge-budget-deficits-and-scaring-off-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦重掌巴西政权已经快两年了。对于投资者来说，前景十分黯淡。巴西货币贬值，政府债券收益率上升，股市涨幅仅为其他新兴市场的一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/lula-is-running-huge-budget-deficits-and-scaring-off-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳总统候选人力争让债务缠身的国家实现 6% 的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/ghana-s-bawumia-unveils-election-manifesto-with-focus-on-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳副总统马哈穆杜·巴武米亚 (Mahamudu Bawumia) 是 12 月选举中竞选最高职位的弱势一方，他制定了雄心勃勃的计划，旨在将经济增长率提高到平均 6%，并减少深陷债务危机的国家的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/ghana-s-bawumia-unveils-election-manifesto-with-focus-on-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗支持的激进组织声称在特拉维夫发动自杀式袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hamas-islamic-jihad-claim-suicide-operation-in-tel-aviv-sunday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的巴勒斯坦组织声称对周日发生在特拉维夫的“自杀式任务”负责，并警告说，只要以色列继续在加沙地带开展军事行动，他们还会采取进一步的类似行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hamas-islamic-jihad-claim-suicide-operation-in-tel-aviv-sunday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚总统将推迟提前投票，局势进一步恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bulgaria-president-to-delay-snap-vote-over-interim-minister-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚总统鲁门·拉德夫意外拒绝批准新临时内阁并表示将推迟提前选举，这导致保加利亚的政治动荡加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bulgaria-president-to-delay-snap-vote-over-interim-minister-pick</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称乌克兰寻求俄罗斯攻击缓冲区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-seeks-russia-buffer-zone-with-incursion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，乌克兰正寻求削弱俄罗斯发动袭击的能力，包括在俄罗斯领土上建立缓冲区，以应对基辅军队继续跨境入侵库尔斯克地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-seeks-russia-buffer-zone-with-incursion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 07:37:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国采取措施缓解因暴乱而加剧的监狱过度拥挤问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/uk-takes-emergency-action-to-ease-prison-crowding-after-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[目前，英国监狱系统已开始接收数百名因最近的骚乱而被起诉的嫌疑人，为此，基尔·斯塔默领导的英国政府批准采取紧急措施，以防止英格兰北部监狱过度拥挤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/uk-takes-emergency-action-to-ease-prison-crowding-after-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:16:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯试图达成停火协议，以色列与哈马斯谈判陷入僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/netanyahu-seeks-to-place-responsibility-with-hamas-for-a-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的高级外交官抵达该地区敦促达成协议，以色列和哈马斯互相指责对方拖延停火和人质协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/netanyahu-seeks-to-place-responsibility-with-hamas-for-a-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:31:35 GMT</pubDate>
